That's reasonable.

785
00:48:18,800 --> 00:48:20,631
It's our age.

786
00:48:31,600 --> 00:48:33,238
Oh, Suzanne!

787
00:48:34,200 --> 00:48:35,553
Maurice ...

788
00:48:37,120 --> 00:48:37,996
Suzanne!

789
00:48:50,160 --> 00:48:52,276
The demand for umbrellas in India

790
00:48:52,520 --> 00:48:53,555
is up 14% per year.

791
00:48:53,760 --> 00:48:57,036
By increasing our sales by 25%
we'd get ...

792
00:48:57,240 --> 00:49:00,118
43.70% of the market.
Exactly.

793
00:49:00,320 --> 00:49:02,914
Not to mention the climate forecasts


794
00:49:03,120 --> 00:49:05,270
which predict an increase
in rain.

795
00:49:05,520 --> 00:49:07,317
Where it falls,
there we are!

796
00:49:07,520 --> 00:49:11,877
So if I count
one umbrella for every two households,

797
00:49:12,080 --> 00:49:14,753
knowing that there are 110 million people
that's ...

798
00:49:14,960 --> 00:49:17,838
22 million brollies.
Yes, 22 million.

799
00:49:18,480 --> 00:49:21,836
It would be a big market.
The Japanese are already established.

800
00:49:22,080 --> 00:49:24,389
Set all that out clearly for me

801
00:49:24,600 --> 00:49:28,832
and do me a summary
for the sales manager.

802
00:49:29,040 --> 00:49:32,077
And for my daughter too.
Ah? Okay.

803
00:49:32,280 --> 00:49:34,953
What time does my husband arrive?
Ten past eleven.

804
00:49:35,160 --> 00:49:38,436
Make sure I don't
have any appointments.

805
00:49:39,920 --> 00:49:42,718
What's Laurent
going to show us?

806
00:49:44,120 --> 00:49:45,348
Good morning, madame.

807
00:49:46,120 --> 00:49:48,350
Hello, darling.

808
00:49:48,560 --> 00:49:50,755
Good morning, my friends.
Good morning Madame Pujol.

809
00:49:50,960 --> 00:49:52,996
How are you all?
Very well.

810
00:49:53,200 --> 00:49:56,476
Call me Suzanne.
So?

811
00:49:56,680 --> 00:49:59,353
We've finished the sketches
for the new collection

812
00:49:59,560 --> 00:50:02,552
which could be called
The Rainbow Collection.

813
00:50:02,760 --> 00:50:04,478
What a lovely idea!

814
00:50:04,680 --> 00:50:07,114
One, two, three.

815
00:50:08,520 --> 00:50:11,034
Oh! This one's very pretty.

816
00:50:11,240 --> 00:50:12,878
I love these colours.

817
00:50:13,120 --> 00:50:15,270
What d'you think, Nadège?
A bit garish.

818
00:50:15,520 --> 00:50:18,318
But it's the fashion.
It's so original.

819
00:50:18,560 --> 00:50:20,039
Look, Maman. A surprise.

820
00:50:20,240 --> 00:50:21,992
The Kandinsky line.

821
00:50:22,240 --> 00:50:24,879
Oh! It's daring.
That's the high end.

822
00:50:25,080 --> 00:50:26,672
At the same time 
revolutionary.

823
00:50:26,880 --> 00:50:28,916
With acknowlegements to Monsieur Babin.

824
00:50:29,120 --> 00:50:30,997
On another tack, we've begun sketching

825
00:50:31,200 --> 00:50:34,431
for the waxed line
But we haven't got far yet.

826
00:50:34,640 --> 00:50:38,599
Your father 'll be happy and 
proud of your initiatives.

827
00:50:38,800 --> 00:50:39,596
Hopefully.

828
00:50:39,840 --> 00:50:42,912
They are amazing.
It surprised me, anyway.

829
00:50:43,840 --> 00:50:47,913
Mama, can I talk to you?
Can it wait till this afternoon?

830
00:50:48,120 --> 00:50:50,156
I want to see you
before Papa arrives.

831
00:50:54,720 --> 00:50:58,076
Madame Pujol's office.

832
00:50:58,280 --> 00:51:00,032
I'll be there in 5 minutes.

833
00:51:00,240 --> 00:51:03,232
You're not expected 'til tomorrow.

834
00:51:03,440 --> 00:51:05,749
Yes, yes. Okay, I'm coming.

835
00:51:13,280 --> 00:51:17,398
I have a report that Jean-Charles did for me
that's absolutely wonderful.

836
00:51:17,600 --> 00:51:20,068
Feeling better with him!
I told you so.

837
00:51:20,280 --> 00:51:24,319
This report gives us ideas
on the future of the factory.

838
00:51:24,520 --> 00:51:25,873
Among other things,

839
00:51:26,080 --> 00:51:28,753
reduce staff and relocation to Tunisia

840
00:51:28,960 --> 00:51:31,793
to increase
our profits by 35%.

841
00:51:32,000 --> 00:51:34,116
Can you imagine?
I'll read it tonight.

842
00:51:34,360 --> 00:51:35,793
Have you had any results?

843
00:51:36,040 --> 00:51:38,554
Yes. I hope I'm not
pregnant again.

844
00:51:38,800 --> 00:51:41,234
You told me ...
Are you sure it's his?

845
00:51:41,480 --> 00:51:42,549
What do you take me for?

846
00:51:42,800 --> 00:51:43,835
Excuse me.

847
00:51:44,080 --> 00:51:45,832
You should thank Jean-Charles,

848
00:51:46,080 --> 00:51:49,356
But the priority,
is to restore a harmonious social climate

849
00:51:49,560 --> 00:51:51,391
within the factory.

850
00:51:51,640 --> 00:51:54,598
But we must also
look ahead and modernize.

851
00:51:54,840 --> 00:51:58,276
But modernise without layoffs.

852
00:51:58,480 --> 00:52:01,631
When'll you stop
listening to your communist?

853
00:52:01,840 --> 00:52:06,197
The deputy mayor has nothing to do
with my management of the plant.

854
00:52:06,440 --> 00:52:08,271
I happened to see him

855
00:52:08,480 --> 00:52:11,074
and he was opposed
to my initiatives.

856
00:52:11,320 --> 00:52:13,390
Then read this report.

857
00:52:13,640 --> 00:52:15,517
I'll read it... I promise.

858
00:52:19,520 --> 00:52:22,830
I remember how my papa
was loved by his workers.

859
00:52:23,360 --> 00:52:26,193
He led the plant
for over 40 years

860
00:52:26,400 --> 00:52:30,075
and never a single day
stop working, even in 1936.

861
00:52:31,160 --> 00:52:33,071
Workers
retiring,

862
00:52:33,280 --> 00:52:37,319
were given slippers,
an numbered umbrella 

863
00:52:37,520 --> 00:52:41,559
and his autographed photo.

864
00:52:41,800 --> 00:52:44,837
Alas, now we're in 1977.

865
00:52:46,200 --> 00:52:48,111
I haven't forgotten.

866
00:52:57,440 --> 00:52:59,670
Hello, Monsieur Pujol.
Hello, Nadège.

867
00:52:59,880 --> 00:53:02,189
How are you?
Very good.

868
00:53:02,800 --> 00:53:05,837
I've missed you.
Me too, Robert.

869
00:53:06,320 --> 00:53:10,552
One second, please.
I have something to ask you.

870
00:53:10,760 --> 00:53:14,833
About the problem of structure...
the first stand ...

871
00:53:15,080 --> 00:53:17,799
Ah, you do it for me.
- Stop.

872
00:53:18,000 --> 00:53:21,515
They might surprise us.
They're eating.

873
00:53:21,720 --> 00:53:24,917
No. There was a meeting
in the boardroom

874
00:53:25,120 --> 00:53:28,078
on new development strategies.

875
00:53:28,280 --> 00:53:30,236
"Development"?
My arse...yes!

876
00:53:30,440 --> 00:53:32,670
Why you haven't you told me 
about this?

877
00:53:32,880 --> 00:53:35,394
And my mail?
A postcard!

878
00:53:35,600 --> 00:53:39,559
I didn't have my favorite little secretary
 in my bag.

879
00:53:39,760 --> 00:53:43,070
Enough of this now!
Aren't you happy to see me?

880
00:53:43,280 --> 00:53:45,669
Not like this.
I am no longer the same.

881
00:53:45,880 --> 00:53:49,077
What are you doing, Nadège?
I changed.

882
00:53:49,320 --> 00:53:52,551
I am a new woman
thanks to the woman in charge.

883
00:53:52,800 --> 00:53:54,472
You're having it off with her too?

884
00:53:54,720 --> 00:53:56,312
She, she respects me.

885
00:53:56,560 --> 00:53:58,312
Come and finish
what we started.

886
00:53:58,520 --> 00:54:00,875
I'm aroused!
I've made my decision.

887
00:54:01,080 --> 00:54:03,753
If we're to continue
you've  got to leave your wife for me.

888
00:54:04,000 --> 00:54:05,479
Leave Suzanne?
You're mad?

889
00:54:05,680 --> 00:54:07,875
I've always cheated.
It suits her.

890
00:54:08,080 --> 00:54:10,435
I don't want to live
in the shade.

891
00:54:10,640 --> 00:54:13,677
I won't be tropohy wife number 2.


892
00:54:13,880 --> 00:54:15,472
Nadège!

893
00:54:18,720 --> 00:54:20,233
Suzanne!

894
00:54:20,480 --> 00:54:23,711
You're back?
Just got in.

895
00:54:24,480 --> 00:54:26,948
I wanted to celebrate your return.

896
00:54:27,160 --> 00:54:29,037
I wanted to give you
a surprise.

897
00:54:29,240 --> 00:54:33,358
And I brought a gift from
Greece for the umbrella queen .

898
00:54:33,560 --> 00:54:36,279
You thought of me?
You've changed the decor?

899
00:54:36,480 --> 00:54:38,311
I added
a little color.

900
00:54:38,520 --> 00:54:41,671
It's beautiful!
I knew it would please you.

901
00:54:41,880 --> 00:54:45,395
You're spoiled, Madame Pujol.
He's not mean to me.

902
00:54:45,600 --> 00:54:47,670
Are they
real diamonds?

903
00:54:47,880 --> 00:54:50,394
Here, I thought of you too.
Really?

904
00:54:55,960 --> 00:54:57,439
Turkish delight?

905
00:54:57,680 --> 00:54:59,511
Turkish delight? I love it.

906
00:54:59,760 --> 00:55:01,955
Thanks from my diet.
Leave us please, Nadège.

907
00:55:02,160 --> 00:55:03,434
Very good.

908
00:55:07,520 --> 00:55:09,795
If you can assist
a man in trouble

909
00:55:10,040 --> 00:55:13,077
without becoming skeptical
as to his quality,

910
00:55:13,320 --> 00:55:15,151
if you know how to be beautiful
without being boring,

911
00:55:15,360 --> 00:55:17,555
if you can be strong
without being impatient

912
00:55:17,760 --> 00:55:19,751
experienced
without ageing,

913
00:55:19,960 --> 00:55:22,394
friendly and smiling
even to a savage

914
00:55:22,640 --> 00:55:24,835
if you know how to type,
shorthand, phone,

915
00:55:25,080 --> 00:55:27,435
if you can give birth
during lunchtime

916
00:55:27,640 --> 00:55:31,952
then better than architect,
engineer or minister,

917
00:55:32,960 --> 00:55:36,475
forever protected by the peaks
where it shines,

918
00:55:36,680 --> 00:55:38,033
thou shalt be secretary,

919
00:55:38,280 --> 00:55:39,474
my daughter.

920
00:55:44,720 --> 00:55:46,392
She's completely crazy.

921
00:55:46,600 --> 00:55:49,239
But no.
Me, I like her.

922
00:55:49,440 --> 00:55:51,670
You saw her new hairstyle?
No.

923
00:55:51,880 --> 00:55:54,348
Give her a compliment.
You know me ...

924
00:55:54,560 --> 00:55:56,755
You could force yourself.


925
00:55:56,960 --> 00:55:58,234
I can't put a finger on it,

926
00:55:58,440 --> 00:56:01,238
I don't know what you've done,

927
00:56:01,440 --> 00:56:03,556
but I think you're better than before.

928
00:56:04,880 --> 00:56:07,519
Kiss me?
I am your husband.

929
00:56:07,720 --> 00:56:10,837
You'll have spent 30 years
keeping that in mind.

930
00:56:11,080 --> 00:56:14,470
Like when I was pissed off
during the cruise.

931
00:56:14,680 --> 00:56:17,399
But it was good for you.
You're fit,

932
00:56:17,640 --> 00:56:19,870
tanned ...
I've got energy to spare.

933
00:56:20,080 --> 00:56:22,514
Holidays over
for the guys too.

934
00:56:22,720 --> 00:56:25,951
What holidays?
Last 3 months at the factory.

935
00:56:26,160 --> 00:56:28,196
It hasn't been a holiday.

936
00:56:28,400 --> 00:56:30,516
We even caught up with the strike days.
No kidding!

937
00:56:30,760 --> 00:56:33,877
You received the reports?
Absolutely.

938
00:56:34,080 --> 00:56:36,389
You've looked after everything
I was concerned about.

939
00:56:36,600 --> 00:56:38,477
No, Robert, I assure you.

940
00:56:38,680 --> 00:56:40,955
After the bad times
things have

941
00:56:41,160 --> 00:56:43,196
gone well,
and even very well.

942
00:56:43,400 --> 00:56:45,311
Still, after a strike.

943
00:56:45,520 --> 00:56:49,149
You sat in my chair,
you put on your innocent air,

944
00:56:49,360 --> 00:56:52,432
you've generously
accepted all the changes...

945
00:56:52,640 --> 00:56:53,755
You've been remarkable.

946
00:56:54,000 --> 00:56:56,673
The "Madame CEO" plaque will come off the door

947
00:56:56,880 --> 00:56:59,792
and Madame will return to her
domestic activities.

948
00:57:00,000 --> 00:57:01,558
