950
00:57:04,160 --> 00:57:05,957
Me.

951
00:57:06,160 --> 00:57:08,037
An brief analysis of the situation.....

952
00:57:08,240 --> 00:57:12,233
I represent an employer with a smile,
fair, warm.

953
00:57:12,440 --> 00:57:15,955
I even managed to persuade
your children to join the factory.

954
00:57:16,160 --> 00:57:17,513
