of the shares.

959
00:57:31,560 --> 00:57:33,312
My sister inherited some.

960
00:57:33,520 --> 00:57:36,557
Add to that the 20%
of Laurent and Joel,

961
00:57:36,760 --> 00:57:38,591
more small shareholders.

962
00:57:38,800 --> 00:57:40,950
In total,
I've got 55% under my belt.

963
00:57:41,160 --> 00:57:43,799
You don't even have that 45%.
Suzanne!

964
00:57:44,000 --> 00:57:47,709
But I'll defend
your interests like a lioness!

965
00:57:47,920 --> 00:57:50,229
