for yourself!

966
00:57:50,440 --> 00:57:53,034
Golf, fishing,
hunting, bridge ...

967
00:57:53,240 --> 00:57:56,516
You won't miss anything!
So that's me now, the trophy wife?

968
00:57:56,720 --> 00:57:57,709
Sort of.

969
00:57:57,920 --> 00:57:59,990
But you'll soon get the hang of it.

970
00:58:00,200 --> 00:58:00,950
Come in.

971
00:58:02,440 --> 00:58:03,919
Papa? You're back?

972
00:58:04,160 --> 00:58:05,559
Hello.

973
00:58:07,960 --> 00:58:09,029
