974
00:58:09,240 --> 00:58:11,993
Your tricks won't work.

975
00:58:12,200 --> 00:58:14,555
I haven't had the last word.

976
00:58:14,800 --> 00:58:17,189
Laurent has had nothing to do
with all this.

977
00:58:17,400 --> 00:58:20,472
He runs the design department of
Pujol umbrellas ...

978
00:58:20,720 --> 00:58:23,678
I don't give a fuck!
I want my place back!

979
00:58:23,880 --> 00:58:26,394
He's done a great job...
remarkable!

980
00:58:26,600 --> 00:58:29,319
Forget it, Maman...
papa won't change.

981
00:58:29,520 --> 00:58:32,990
I'll miss my train.
Don't be late on our account.

982
00:58:33,200 --> 00:58:35,714
Hi to Floriane and kisses from me.

983
00:58:37,080 --> 00:58:38,593
Hang in there.

984
00:58:41,960 --> 00:58:43,109
"Floriane"?

985
00:58:43,360 --> 00:58:45,715
The Marquiset girl.
He'll see her in Paris.

986
00:58:45,960 --> 00:58:49,157
They seem
to get along wonderfully.

987
00:58:49,360 --> 00:58:50,759
You're crazy.

988
00:58:50,960 --> 00:58:54,236
You've forgotten what I told you?
It still gives me a pain in the gut.

989
00:58:54,440 --> 00:58:56,271
They can no longer see each other.

990
00:58:56,520 --> 00:58:59,751
They're brother and sister.     
You don't say!

991
00:58:59,960 --> 00:59:03,475

You're so respectable!

992
00:59:03,680 --> 00:59:04,430
It bores me

993
00:59:04,680 --> 00:59:09,117
to tell it like that ...
Don't get angry.

994
00:59:09,360 --> 00:59:10,270
Go ahead, speak.

995
00:59:10,520 --> 00:59:13,990
Laurent and Floriane can marry
with impunity.

996
00:59:14,240 --> 00:59:15,958
But I'm telling you ...

997
00:59:16,200 --> 00:59:18,077
