00:59:26,520 --> 00:59:29,114
You're lying.

1002
00:59:30,360 --> 00:59:31,918
I'll have to go.

1003
00:59:32,120 --> 00:59:34,190
Put yourself in my shoes.

1004
00:59:34,440 --> 00:59:37,876
I was young, quite cute
completely neglected

1005
00:59:38,120 --> 00:59:40,839
