1006
00:59:41,080 --> 00:59:42,798
I regret nothing.

1007
00:59:43,000 --> 00:59:44,672
And I fixed your mistake.

1008
00:59:44,920 --> 00:59:47,434
Who...who've you deceived me with?

1009
00:59:47,680 --> 00:59:50,877
There are limits....
Just calm down.

1010
00:59:51,120 --> 00:59:53,634
My factory, my wife, my son ...

1011
00:59:53,840 --> 00:59:57,389
It's the end of the lunch break.
It was good to see you again.

1012
00:59:57,640 --> 00:59:59,870
We still have
things to discuss.

1013
01:00:00,080 --> 01:00:02,230
I must get back to work.

1014
01:00:02,440 --> 01:00:05,238
There's a quiche
for you in the fridge.

1015
01:00:05,440 --> 01:00:08,193
